{"type": "article", "id": 3010, "title": "Cappellini 2014 Peg 系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-23T07:28:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143640oxi35F7gq614wkte.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t2013 年，日本设计师 Nendo 为意大利家居品牌 Cappellini 设计了既柔软又舒适的家具系列 Peg，今年 Nendo 为这一系列又添新品，包括沙发、桌几、扶手椅以及镜子等，力图表现出完整的居家感受。为了展现 Peg 柔软舒适的一面，新作的线条细节多呈现出圆角的温暖感觉，沙发、桌椅的腿部也被做出了木桩的质朴之感。这一系列的作品已在今年的米兰家具展上展出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061436381Ncj5UqsKQWR2vlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.059375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143638Io3zFByDh0ZVAOYg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143639vHFXCyIpaAzJoEQ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143639SKewokQEFmChPUsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143639pC2lOERG59XVYx4n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.075\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061436401VhBK3rCY40etv2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}